FL,370,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F369A1778083869
OL,3,CFive arrested after contaminated drugs
OL,4,Coverdoses
OL,6,FFollowing these incidents, two
OL,7,Fwarrants were carried out at two
OL,8,Faddresses, one on Hainton Avenue and a
OL,9,Fsecond on Daubney Street, which led to
OL,10,Fthe arrests.
OL,12,FChief Superintendent Sharon Philpott
OL,13,Fsaid the force is working with the
OL,14,Flocal authority, drugs and alcohol
OL,15,Ftreatment services and the hospital
OL,16,Ftrusts to "provide the appropriate
OL,17,Fsupport."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
